---
---
<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
      
      <!-- Text Content (Left) -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-800 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block">About taxomade&trade;</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight">Your partner for relocation and taxes in Southern Europe.</h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg text-slate-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          <p>Moving to a new country as a remote worker or freelancer can be complicated, expensive, and stressful. Language barriers, confusing tax laws, and slow bureaucracy get in the way of a smooth start.</p>
          <p>Taxomade&trade; is the service we wished existed when we relocated ourselves — several times. It's a simple, digital-first partner that handles your visa, tax registration, and ongoing bookkeeping entirely for you. And we don't disappear once you've arrived — we stay your long-term partner for anything that comes up.</p>
          <p>Working with trusted local accountants, we keep everything transparent, affordable, and fully remote. You focus on your work and life under the Mediterranean sun — we take care of the paperwork.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Profile/Steckbrief -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 max-w-sm mx-auto">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">At a glance</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3 shrink-0 text-slate-400">✓</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 block text-sm">Focus</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Freelancers & Remote Workers</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3 shrink-0 text-slate-400">📱</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 block text-sm">Operations</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">100% Digital & English-speaking</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="mr-3 shrink-0 text-slate-400">⚡</span>
              <div>
                <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 block text-sm">Mission</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Making bureaucracy simple.</span>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image (Right) -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative mt-8 lg:mt-0 bg-white p-4 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-800 rounded-3xl transform translate-x-4 translate-y-4 opacity-10"></div>
        <img src="/images/founders.png" alt="Leonard and Manoli, Managing Partners of taxomade&trade;" class="rounded-2xl shadow-md relative z-10 w-full h-auto object-cover" />
        
        <div class="flex justify-between mt-6 relative z-10 text-sm">
          <div class="flex-1 border-r border-slate-200 pr-4 text-right">
            <strong class="text-slate-900 block text-base">Leonard</strong>
            <span class="text-slate-500 italic block mb-2">Managing Partner, Taxomade&trade;</span>
            <span class="text-slate-600 block text-xs">🗣️ English, German, Spanish</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 pl-4 text-left">
            <strong class="text-slate-900 block text-base">Manoli</strong>
            <span class="text-slate-500 italic block mb-2">Managing Partner, Taxomade&trade;</span>
            <span class="text-slate-600 block text-xs">🗣️ German, English</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
